17 2. The misuse of office for pecuniary or material gain or for
18 personal advantage for self or another;
19 3. A violation of the laws or rules governing the practice of
20 alcohol and drug counseling; or
21 4. Conviction of a felony as verified by a certified copy of
22 the record of the court of conviction.
